<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201009/9e54898bef3a4225a773010cee594091.png" /></p>
<p>创业板指收涨3.99%：</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201009/74d322a174cf40b5a2f998d398685396.png" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
